{$begin-section} 6
{$sub-head} Aufgabe 6

Noll     = .4 * 400,000
Ravens   = .4 * 200,000
Abzug    = Noll + Ravens = 24,000
Restumme = 72,000 - Abzug = 72,000 - 24,000 = 48,000

Noll   = Restumme / 2 + Noll   = 16,000 + 24,000 = 40,000 €
Ravens = Restumme / 2 + Ravens =  8,000 + 24,000 = 32,000 €
